title: Rizzoli and Isles Seasons 1-4
description:
All fifty two episodes currently released on DVD for Rizzoli and Isles.

Synopsis: Star homicide detective Jane Rizzoli (Angie Harmon) and her braniac medical examiner best friend (Sasha Alexander) work together to solve murders that happen in their backyard, Boston Massachusetts, and to do their best to work through the life that happens along the way.

Disclaimer: I didn't rip the videos. I just assembled the various current seasons into one, easy to download, bundle.
